      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms at any time. Changes take effect when posted on this page. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@apotidev.org">info@apotidev.org</a>.</p>
